<template>
    <section class="flexCenter pages-container">
                
        <Profile/>
        <PrivateWall/>
        <Actu/>

    </section>
</template>


<script>
    import Actu from './Actu.vue'
    import PrivateWall from './PrivateWall.vue'
    import Profile from './Profile.vue'
    // import Publish from './Publish.vue'

    export default {
        name: 'PagesSwap',
        
        components: {
            Actu,
            PrivateWall,
            Profile,
            // Publish,
        },
    }
</script>


<style scoped>
    .pages-container {
        position: relative;
        height: 500px;
        margin: 5px;
        margin-top: 0;
    }
</style>


<style>
    .flow {
        justify-content: flex-start !important;
        overflow: scroll;
        height: 410px;
        width: 95% !important;
        margin-left: 25px;
    }


    /* ======== Pages Swap => Button ======== */
    .actu-btn,
    .private-wall-btn,
    .profile-btn {
        position: absolute;
        height: 40px;
        width: 32%;
        top: -40px;
        border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;

        font-family: "Roboto-Medium";
        line-height: 100%;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 120%;
    }


    /* ======== Pages Swap => Page ======== */
    .actu,
    .private-wall,
    .profile {
        position: absolute;
        height: 90%;
        width: 96% !important;
        top: 43px;
        left: 0;
    }
</style>
